Calculate the Lebesgue integral of the function \( f:(0,\infty)\rightarrow [0,\infty) \) defined by:
\[
f(x)=\begin{cases}
|\sin(x)| & \text{if } x\in \mathbb{Q},\\
4x & \text{if } x\in[0,1]\backslash \mathbb{Q},\\
0 & \text{if } x\in (1,\infty)\backslash \mathbb{Q}
\end{cases}
\]
Determine \( \int_{(0,\infty)} f \, d\lambda \).

