For which two-digit numbers \( N \) does the following method yield the correct result when dividing an arbitrary number \( A \) by \( N \)?

1) Divide \( A \) by the sum of the digits of \( N \);
2) Divide \( A \) by the product of the digits of \( N \);
3) Subtract the second result from the first.

